ygData.messageBody:
Gee patty,

Really sorry to hear about that...i know how that feels all to well, The
other day My guild was killing sand giants in the oasis and i was in the
background watching with my cleric and throwing in the occasional heal..when
all of a sudden a second giant decided to jump in and help his brother.
needless to say my senses were knocked out of me and strewn all across the
Dunes. Sigh there is nothing more embarassing than having a giant sneak up
on you!


John Zwanenburg
Tips Support/Support Sipt
